Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:35.58,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Risa, after thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:39.02,Title,,0,0,0,,Complete Despair!\N A Love Revival With the Ex?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:38.05,Superscript,,0,0,0,,...I've realized that you're all I think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:38.99,Superscript,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Cain-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:45.83,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Cain Osugi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:45.83,Superscript,,0,0,0,,[ Hahaha .  .  . ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is straining my heartstrings...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, we've come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for Hatsumode.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.59,Superscript,,0,0,0,,SUMIYOSHI GRAND SHRINE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, there are a lot of people here for New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are darling and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end there was no miracle, and another year passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be as easy as it is in a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is straining my heartstrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The way Otani gets me so worked up every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...it kinda pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Grant me happiness this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is funny about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was paying you a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You were definitely making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Noisy, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That grin of yours is pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww, oww, oww, oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pretend we don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See what you've done?\N People are laughing at us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am just a comedienne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, should we go our separate ways from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up. You need to do your best from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That chest you didn't reveal over Christmas, reveal it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For a girl, you sure say some shameless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with this lack of motivation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A maiden's heart is fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a rare opportunity. Why not keep it at it until morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Until morning? There you go saying shameless things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun, you'd better walk Risa home properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Nobu-chan say to you just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should we do now? Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's think of something to do until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Video game arcades and karaokes places are open so let's just stay out all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is New Years, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. So that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the karaoke place by the train station has heaps of Umibouzu songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Let's go for all-night karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hokkaido is cold but there's no point in worrying about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could call you but we use the same cellphone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Family discount plants are pretty awesome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if tears of anger come,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not interested riding around in a fancy boat{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or taking an expensive looking dog for a walk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not pale enough to need to use a parasol!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you don't have what it takes to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the first thing I'm hearing from you this semester is this stupidity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent all night getting worked up singing karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're still concerned about that Kanzaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki-san is super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's even possible for Otani to like a girl like me....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been rejected once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you decided to keep trying anyway, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,An ex is just an ex, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your good points too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you think of any at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're funny! You're very funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Otani-kun is always saying so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not use your comedic skills to win his love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I am funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Comedy... for love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to react to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'm just trying to tug at your heart strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa is so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is energetic, so early in the semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, how are things on Otani-kun's end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he said anything about Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, what was that "ah!" just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Third-year students should remember that entrance exams are just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I get more of a romantic mood going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly would that be like between us, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, that's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall something that happened back when I was a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssssh! Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're saying Kanzaki-san and her giant boyfriend broke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Nakao-chi's info isn't always  reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This time it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He bumped into Kanzaki-san the other day, and heard it directly from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't ask why they broke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...but apparently it happened just before Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why she didn't come to the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So, does Otani know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We don't want him to get any ideas. So we haven't told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, last time Kanzaki-san said she just wanted to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and look how worked up he got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,While Kanzaki-san's heart is still wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...if only Otani-kun should happen to say some kind words to her....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Her heartstrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And up against a girl like her, Otani-kun would...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His heartstrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, who was the one who told me "An ex is just an ex, after all"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we shouldn't let news of Kanzaki-san's breakup reach Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bring up Kanzaki-san in front of Otani at all, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we need to take countermeasures to prevent the two of them meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! She appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to see Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Did he already leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He did. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he say he'd be right back after dropping by the staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, we can't let them meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's already gone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? This crushing guilt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart... My heart hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you two attend the basketball club's Christmas party, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that a lot of Atsushi-kun's friends went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought you might have gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She calls him "Atsushi-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, everyone is getting together next Sunday to play basketball again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome to come along if you'd like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be going to, Kanzaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to surround myself with people in a cheery environment right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth be told, that tugged at my heartstrings just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the thing about the breakup was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, could you please let Atsushi-kun know about basketball on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be on my way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing saying a thing like that so casually?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She said they're gonna play basketball again. Kanzaki-san and Otani-kun will meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone... Someone save me! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I guess I am just a comedienne, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An impression of Kanzaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She dropped by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She said there's going to be another basketball get-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Nakao already told me about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She already knew that darling would tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That means she came in person just to see Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are going to come along too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If Otani-kun is going, it'll bother you if you don't go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine her making a face like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and saying, "I just broke up with my boyfriend. I'm so lonely..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy would want to do something about that, wouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you whispering about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really bad this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's here! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We've been waiting for you, Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-These people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. They're planning on getting Otani-kun and Kanzaki-san back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They definitely know about Kanzaki-san's break-up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki-san is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so obviously lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's exuding an aura that says "Comfort me."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, get Otani-kun's attention before he's swallowed up by that aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean "get his attention"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you have to, keep them from talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You trying to pick a fight, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Teach me how to play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun, look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanzaki-san seems really down for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go on over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ask her yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can walk over there on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to play basketball later, Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... It's just, you don't seem well at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to witness the moment they get back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, fight-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So, how's the giant... I mean, your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We broke up, not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm gonna go home, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I just want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we see each other again sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, they're probably locked in the storage closet like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the door is opened, they'll probably be together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's me trapped in there with him, all he can do is derive amusement from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, a comedienne is no match for an ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of that Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay in a place like this, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What... are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking "Maybe Koizumi is crying again," or something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. What an ugly expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kanzaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I last spoke to Kanzaki. It was pretty exhausting, for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there'll be snowdrifts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone like you is more suited for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go home, let's go to that karaoke place by the train station again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time Otani says or does something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...I end up going to heaven, or hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole world has been revolving around Otani, going round and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! I haven't said anything bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You seriously piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inviting you for some fun karaoke... What's that attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You amazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can we see each other again sometime?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I don't think I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's this one hopeless idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...who'll probably end up crying if I see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I don't think I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The second Valentine's episode is all about the winning chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Winning?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, are you expecting to win a kiss or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! She's acting weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Recapture Love! Improve as a Girl With Winning Chocolate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
